{"tid":777394,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"2018年 Linux 遊戲推介","createTime":"2018-08-13T01:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T02:25:08.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"76b3b3dc3de834d1afa489e23cf321e3fbb4e922","tid":777394,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T01:01:06.000Z","msg":"2018年能在Linux上玩的遊戲：動作類<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.linuxpilot.com/2018_linuxg_ames_action\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linuxpilot.com%2F2018_linuxg_ames_action&d=%2B5Q0IrOHhkUFI4%2F8znlASMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=10e80d2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.linuxpilot.com/2018_linuxg_ames_action</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年能在Linux上玩的遊戲：策略類<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.linuxpilot.com/2018_linux_games_stg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linuxpilot.com%2F2018_linux_games_stg&d=%2B5Q0IrOHhkUFI4%2F8znlASMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e895d54d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.linuxpilot.com/2018_linux_games_stg</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年能在Linux上玩的遊戲：角色扮演類<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.linuxpilot.com/2018_linux_games_rpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linuxpilot.com%2F2018_linux_games_rpg&d=%2B5Q0IrOHhkUFI4%2F8znlASMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=5ffc4bd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.linuxpilot.com/2018_linux_games_rpg</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年能在Linux上玩的遊戲：運動及模擬類<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.linuxpilot.com/2018_linux_games_sim\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linuxpilot.com%2F2018_linux_games_sim&d=%2B5Q0IrOHhkUFI4%2F8znlASMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=a157fc91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.linuxpilot.com/2018_linux_games_sim</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年能在Linux上玩的遊戲：冒險類<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.linuxpilot.com/2018_linux_games_adv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linuxpilot.com%2F2018_linux_games_adv&d=%2B5Q0IrOHhkUFI4%2F8znlASMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=8ba674e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.linuxpilot.com/2018_linux_games_adv</a>"},{"pid":"8c10c8113c4ef77469b9f3473adfc1be8a4d2eeb","tid":777394,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T01:03:51.000Z","msg":"提起電腦遊戲平台，人們十居其九都會想到Windows。但現在情況卻不一樣，Steam商店裡現在有許多支援Linux的大作，這次就介紹一些動作類的。<br />\n<br />\n數年前Steam for Linux上可玩的遊戲不多，而且並不吸引，但現在很多主流大作都可在Steam for Linux上玩了。首先不能不提的反恐精英：全球攻勢(Counter-Strike: Global Offensive)，它毫無疑問是Steam上支援Linux的最好的FPS遊戲之一。而且支援多人同時玩。它還是電子競技中的一個主流項目。想要提升等級的話，需要在天梯上和其他玩家同台競技，但也可以選擇更加輕鬆的休閒模式。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.linuxpilot.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018_linux_games_action_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linuxpilot.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018_linux_games_action_02.jpg&h=a101f6c0&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n求生之路2(Left 4 Dead 2)這是最受歡迎的殭屍主題多人FPS遊戲之一。在Steam優惠時，價格可以低至1.3美元。它能讓你體會到你在殭屍遊戲中期待的顫慄和刺激。遊戲中的環境包括了沼澤、城市、墓地等等，遊戲中的槍械並不是非常先進，但作為一個老遊戲來說，它已經提供了足夠真實的體驗。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.linuxpilot.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018_linux_games_action_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linuxpilot.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018_linux_games_action_03.jpg&h=6dabf65e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n無主之地 2(Borderlands 2)是個很有意思的FPS遊戲，畫風看上去有些詭異和卡通化，如果你正在尋找一個第一視角的射擊遊戲，它的遊戲體驗可一點也不遜色。如果你在尋找一個好玩而且有很多DLC的Linux遊戲，《無主之地2》絕對是個不錯的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.linuxpilot.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018_linux_games_action_04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linuxpilot.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018_linux_games_action_04.jpg&h=676eff47&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n叛亂(Insurgency)是Steam上又一款支援Linux的優秀FPS遊戲。它從屏幕上去掉了HUD和彈藥數量指示，注重武器和團隊戰術。這也許不是最好的FPS遊戲，但如果你想玩和《三角洲部隊》類似的多人遊戲的話，這絕對是最好的遊戲之一。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.linuxpilot.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018_linux_games_action_05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linuxpilot.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018_linux_games_action_05.jpg&h=abc4ffd9&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"bfd3412cda380659dd8d8116d09ff83291cddea3","tid":777394,"uid":97439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T01:24:07.000Z","msg":"it狗打乜機呀打返code啦"},{"pid":"45e3432190eca90e8e82ec6dbd36e187bde65f63","tid":777394,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T01:40:50.000Z","msg":"rise of the tomb raider"},{"pid":"c727fa20c6f0892dea6ba56a894d160efc7c2838","tid":777394,"uid":38891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T01:45:05.000Z","msg":"battlefield都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef290d122060a1c7abcd0d2b3082a9e09bbb1e71","tid":777394,"uid":95172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:25:08.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}